WEBVTT

00:05:59.911 --> 00:06:02.982
That's something remarkable
about this country.

00:06:03.006 --> 00:06:04.666
In many other countries,

00:06:04.690 --> 00:06:06.561
this driver would have been shot,

00:06:06.585 --> 00:06:08.442
just for bringing his case.

00:06:08.466 --> 00:06:11.395
And more of the point for me,
his lawyer would have been shot.

00:06:11.419 --> 00:06:13.518
But that's what makes America different.

00:06:13.542 --> 00:06:15.542
What makes America special."

